      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chips are cooking, peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>fennel</strong> <strong>seeds</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and grind (or finely chop if you don't have a pestle and mortar) to a fine powder</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1716293767810-x200.jpg",
