            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>beef mince</strong> and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>fennel</strong> <strong>seeds </strong>(not a fan of aniseed? Only add a little!) in a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong> (save the rest for later!), your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>paprika</strong>, <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands is the best way!) – this is your <strong>merguez-style mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1716293772051-x200.jpg",
