        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomato</strong>, <strong>shallot</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>cumin salsa</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>harissa</strong> <strong>paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>mayo</strong> in a separate bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>harissa mayo</strong></p>",
