    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill your <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> with some <strong>harissa</strong> <strong>mayo</strong>, the <strong>merguez-style koftas </strong>and some <strong>cumin</strong> <strong>salsa</strong> – this is your<strong> merguez-style sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>merguez-style sandwich</strong> with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>remaining cumin salsa </strong>and <strong>remaining harissa mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
